            "type": "text",
            "content": "## The Academic Nightmare",
            "style": {
              "fontSize": "xl"
            },
            "position": {
              "area": "header"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "### Sound Familiar?\n\n*\"I had my analysis working perfectly last week, but now it's broken and I can't remember what I changed...\"*",
            "style": {
              "fontSize": "large",
              "color": "#DC2626"
            },
            "position": {
              "area": "content"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "### Common \"Solutions\" That Don't Work:",
            "style": {
              "fontSize": "large",
              "fontWeight": "bold"
            },
            "position": {
              "area": "content",
              "order": 1
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "bullets",
            "items": [
              "`final_analysis_v3_john_comments_FINAL_REAL.py`",
              "\"Dropbox is my version control\"",
              "Emailing files back and forth",
              "\"I'll just remember what I changed\""
            ],
            "bulletStyle": "disc",
            "style": {
              "fontSize": "medium"
            },
            "position": {
              "area": "content",
              "order": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "**The real problem:** No systematic way to track what changed, when, and why",
            "style": {
              "fontSize": "large",
              "color": "#DC2626",
              "fontWeight": "bold"
            },
            "position": {
              "area": "footer"
            }
          }
        ]
      },
